ent-RMCHeadCapTruckerBlue-name = blue trucker hat
ent-RMCHeadCapTruckerBlue-desc = It's a blue trucker hat.
ent-RMCHeadCapWeyamart-name = orange cap
ent-RMCHeadCapWeyamart-desc = It's a baseball style cap in the 'Weyamart' orange color, with the 'Weyamart' logo on the front.
ent-RMCHeadCapPatrol-name = patrol cap
ent-RMCHeadCapPatrol-desc = A casual cap issued as part of the non-combat uniform. While it only protects from the sun, it's much more comfortable than a helmet.
ent-RMCHeadCapPizzaGalaxy-name = Pizza-Galaxy red cap
ent-RMCHeadCapPizzaGalaxy-desc = It's a baseball style cap in a red color, with the 'Pizza-Galaxy' logo on the front.
ent-RMCHeadCapCargo-name = cargo cap
